e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>read<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>close<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>open 함수: data.txt 파일을 객체 형태로 가져와 file이라는 변수에 담아준다.</li>\n<li>read 함수: data.txt 파일에 있는 데이터 전체를 가져온다.</li>\n<li>close 함수: 파일을 닫아준다.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br/><br/></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-실습\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5\" aria-label=\"3 실습 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 실습</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-파일-쓰기-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EC%93%B0%EA%B8%B0-1\" aria-label=\"1 파일 쓰기 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 파일 쓰기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 1. 파일 쓰기</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"data.txt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"w\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>write<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1. 스타트코딩과 함께 파이썬 공부\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>close<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>파일을 실행하면 <code class=\"language-text\">PYTHON_BASIC</code> 폴더에 data.txt 가 생성된다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>경로를 설정하지 않았기 때문에 root 디렉터리 바로 아래에 파일이 생성된 것.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2022-05-16-Python-Photo/2022-05-16-Python-Photo4.png\" alt=\"2022-05-16-Python-Photo4\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<ul>\n<li>data.txt 파일을 open 할 때 경로를 지정해주면 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 1. 파일 쓰기</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./myvenv/Chapter10/data.txt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"w\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>write<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1. 스타트코딩과 함께 파이썬 공부\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token builtin\">file</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>close<span class=\"tok